00:02:34.878 --> 00:02:42.133
Our story starts at the University of Stanford, in the heart of Silicon Valley, in 2003.

00:02:43.108 --> 00:02:47.068
Elizabeth Holmes was a 19 year old chemical engineering

00:02:47.068 --> 00:02:51.718
student, and was exceptionally bright, she was very clever.

00:02:52.738 --> 00:02:59.328
She came from a wealthy background - her father had been an executive at Enron, the company we

